1
00:00:01,130 --> 00:00:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Scarlett's disappeared.</i></font>

2
00:00:04,090 --> 00:00:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's been two days 
since I've seen His Lordship.</i></font>

3
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought she went away because 
she exhausted herself back then,</i></font>

4
00:00:14,190 --> 00:00:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but now I'm sure I was wrong.</i></font>

5
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did she get "fed up" with me, as they say?</i></font>

6
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constance Grail. You have a visitor.</font>

7
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ungrateful girl.</font>

8
00:00:31,670 --> 00:00:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about what you've put me through.</font>

9
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One day, out of the blue, 
I hear my daughter's been arrested,</font>

10
00:00:38,110 --> 00:00:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I rush back to the capital 
only to find her slated for execution.</font>

11
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I'm sorry.</font>

12
00:00:46,470 --> 00:00:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What on earth is going on?</font>

13
00:00:50,010 --> 00:00:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father...</font>

14
00:00:53,650 --> 00:00:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please disown me.</font>

15
00:00:58,970 --> 00:01:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if blame were to spread
to our family because of me?</font>

16
00:01:02,690 --> 00:01:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know much about palace intrigue.</font>

17
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what's happening 
in this country, either.</font>

18
00:01:10,510 --> 00:01:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

19
00:01:12,050 --> 00:01:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I can at least take a stand
 to keep my daughter safe.</font>

20
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But consider the risks!</font>

21
00:01:19,380 --> 00:01:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Constance.</font>

22
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing inspires us like other people,
 no matter the era.</font>

23
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have our own ways of doing things.</font>

24
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Be you sincere."</font>

25
00:01:38,450 --> 00:01:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to see you looking well.</font>

26
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

27
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

28
00:01:55,330 --> 00:01:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want with me, Shoshanna?</font>

29
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Change the people keeping watch.</font>

30
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

31
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They get rough.</font>

32
00:02:07,410 --> 00:02:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows what they'll do 
if someone stands up to them?</font>

33
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So be it.</font>

34
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiriki kirikuku.</font>

35
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lie low and stay calm.</font>

36
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kindly withdraw.</font>

37
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want with us?</font>

38
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to warn you, brave little lady.</font>

39
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless you want to die, 
keep your head down.</font>

40
00:02:54,090 --> 00:02:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awfully kind.</font>

41
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kind?</font>

42
00:02:57,460 --> 00:03:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You and Shoshanna both.</font>

43
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you if ordered to do so.</font>

44
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. And that's why you came, isn't it?</font>

45
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To make sure you won't get that order.</font>

46
00:03:11,450 --> 00:03:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To make sure I'm not killed.</font>

47
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe it!</font>

48
00:03:27,050 --> 00:03:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie, kidnap a prince of Faris?!</font>

49
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now she's to be publicly executed?!</font>

50
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Mylene,</font>

51
00:03:36,010 --> 00:03:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wasn't public execution abolished 
after Scarlett Castiel?</font>

52
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know why?</font>

53
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I believe a citizens' 
group protested.</font>

54
00:03:47,790 --> 00:03:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Violet Association, 
I think it was called.</font>

55
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Violet Association?</font>

56
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Mylene.</font>

57
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where are you going?</font>

58
00:03:55,530 --> 00:03:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To save Connie, of course.</font>

59
00:03:58,810 --> 00:04:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't expect me 
to just sit around weeping.</font>

60
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I've got to take action!</font>

61
00:04:05,970 --> 00:04:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, what an admirable attitude.</font>

62
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spare me your theatrics.</font>

63
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been able to see me 
all along, haven't you?</font>

64
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've no doubt you realized I was there 
since we met at the Grand Merillian.</font>

65
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, you'd never have bothered with
the engagement of a viscount's daughter.</font>

66
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have an excellent memory.</font>

67
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, how heartrending!</font>

68
00:04:49,010 --> 00:04:52,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}10 YEARS AGO</font>

69
00:04:51,330 --> 00:04:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might your humble servant 
assist you in any way?</font>

70
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're an eyesore. Get out of my sight.</font>

71
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what a shame.</font>

72
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should the fancy ever strike you, 
please call upon your humble servant.</font>

73
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. <i>If</i> the fancy strikes.</font>

74
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took ten years, 
but the fancy struck me at last.</font>

75
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

76
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">lend me your aid.</font>

77
00:05:18,650 --> 00:05:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case,</font>

78
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how may this unworthy hog be of service?</font>

79
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By hunting rats.</font>

80
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Royal Highness Prince Theophilis,</font>

81
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kendall Levine of the 
diplomatic service is here.</font>

82
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I thought he left 
on a mission to Adelbide.</font>

83
00:05:43,330 --> 00:05:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regarding that,</font>

84
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he claims there's been
an urgent development.</font>

85
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

86
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show him in.</font>

87
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been ages, Kendall.</font>

88
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What on earth is the matter?</font>

89
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With all due respect,</font>

90
00:05:58,650 --> 00:06:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Ulysses was abducted not 
by Adelbide, but by Daeg Gallus,</font>

91
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Second Prince Roderick 
is in league with them.</font>

92
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

93
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm told that every member of Daeg Gallus</font>

94
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">bears a tattoo of the sun 
somewhere on their bodies.</font>

95
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A tattoo?</font>

96
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never suspected Roderick!</font>

97
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where exactly did you 
get this information?</font>

98
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Third Princess Alexandra.</font>

99
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the ordinary course of events,</font>

100
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was to receive charity from 
Prince Enrique in the near future.</font>

101
00:06:44,790 --> 00:06:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Charity?</font>

102
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed. To facilitate 
spreading the divine word,</font>

103
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we need "contributions" from the faithful
 more substantial than prayers.</font>

104
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt that my brother 
would do any such thing.</font>

105
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be mistaken.</font>

106
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't say.
 Then pray forgive my intrusion.</font>

107
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way...</font>

108
00:07:10,570 --> 00:07:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

109
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you need of divine aid yourself, 
Your Royal Highness?</font>

110
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I...</font>

111
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begging your pardon.</font>

112
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:29,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I interrupting?</font>

113
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. The viscount was just leaving.</font>

114
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you are...?</font>

115
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rufus May.</font>

116
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was recently appointed 
assistant comptroller of the treasury.</font>

117
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, then you're the man 
I've heard about!</font>

118
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever visited my church?</font>

119
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid not, as I'm still new 
to my post. But someday.</font>

120
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, we would be delighted to have you.</font>

121
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do forgive me. 
Static electricity, I suppose.</font>

122
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That, or a whim of the goddesses.</font>

123
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you feel pain?</font>

124
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I do.</font>

125
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:19,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's merely that any pain you inflict 
is the greatest of joys to me.</font>

126
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, did anything strike you?</font>

127
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That man kept his gloves on, 
even when you went to shake hands.</font>

128
00:08:32,490 --> 00:08:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has a sun tattoo on his wrist.</font>

129
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rufus May is a rat. 
Uncover his antecedents at once.</font>

130
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My lady's wish is my command.</font>

131
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then, I can do this much safely...</font>

132
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always feel sleepy 
after using that power.</font>

133
00:08:53,410 --> 00:08:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I feel fine now 
because I kept it weak earlier.</font>

134
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

135
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Causing such phenomena 
consumes a great deal of energy.</font>

136
00:09:02,970 --> 00:09:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would you know about that?</font>

137
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For all my faults, 
I do have the goddesses' favor.</font>

138
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, is revenge your reason 
for remaining in this world?</font>

139
00:09:16,570 --> 00:09:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course it is.</font>

140
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even now?</font>

141
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you getting at?</font>

142
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here and now, are you 
being driven by revenge?</font>

143
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or...</font>

144
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you working to save Constance Grail?</font>

145
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Revenge, naturally.</font>

146
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

147
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe that, to remain 
in the world of the living,</font>

148
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a disembodied soul must have 
some powerful emotion or goal.</font>

149
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I have no doubt that once you feel 
your revenge is complete,</font>

150
00:09:55,050 --> 00:09:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you will return to the gods' side.</font>

151
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please sign our petition 
against this execution!</font>

152
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constance Grail is innocent!</font>

153
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

154
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg you. Lend us your aid.</font>

155
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please help us! We can't save 
my friend Constance Grail</font>

156
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without assistance from
 the right-minded people here!</font>

157
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the meaning of this?</font>

158
00:10:32,370 --> 00:10:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave strict orders to keep 
any petition out of the palace,</font>

159
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and not just commoners have signed this.
 Aristocrats are in on it as well.</font>

160
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then there's this book...</font>

161
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It claims to be by an up-and-coming 
foreign author. Adam Hicks?</font>

162
00:10:51,430 --> 00:10:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's obviously Amelia Hobbes!</font>

163
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A viscount's daughter, lauded as a saint,</font>

164
00:10:56,530 --> 00:10:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">overcomes the gap in status 
to marry a crown prince.</font>

165
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in reality, she's a member 
of a criminal syndicate</font>

166
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:07,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who was born an impoverished orphan.</font>

167
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel as though 
I've heard this plot before.</font>

168
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would they go to such lengths 
for that plain little girl?</font>

169
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what anyone says, 
she <i>will</i> be executed.</font>

170
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Along with that Lucia girl 
the O'Brians adopted.</font>

171
00:11:27,980 --> 00:11:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

172
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

173
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an unpleasant state of affairs.</font>

174
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And just look how those absurd rumors 
spread when one's not looking.</font>

175
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What rumors?</font>

176
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you heard?</font>

177
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean about Constance Grail.</font>

178
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say she can hear 
the voices of the dead</font>

179
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that she's working to clear 
Scarlett Castiel's name.</font>

180
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crown Princess Cecilia?!</font>

181
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say you can speak with the dead.</font>

182
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well...</font>

183
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:07,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liar.</font>

184
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dead don't talk.</font>

185
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have no thoughts.
They just turn to ashes.</font>

186
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's only natural.</i></font>

187
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At least, that's how it was for me.</i></font>

188
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never heard any voices.</i></font>

189
00:12:27,430 --> 00:12:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whose voice...</font>

190
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:30,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}DID YOU WANT TO HEAR?</font>

191
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:39,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}14 YEARS AGO</font>

192
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cici!</font>

193
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go give that back!</font>

194
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why should I, Cess?</font>

195
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Picking pockets is a crime!</font>

196
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting you lead a life</font>

197
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can't be proud of
while I've got my eye on you!</font>

198
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, mister!</font>

199
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it! That's my Cici!</font>

200
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, quit it!</font>

201
00:13:06,380 --> 00:13:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cici, Cess! You're back!</font>

202
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, there's this weird guy here.</font>

203
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weird how?</font>

204
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says he's looking 
for a girl named Cecilia!</font>

205
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's sure got his work 
cut out for him, huh, Cess?</font>

206
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. There's loads of Cecilias, 
even just at our place.</font>

207
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there. You're called Cess?</font>

208
00:13:27,850 --> 00:13:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then is your real name Cecilia?</font>

209
00:13:31,610 --> 00:13:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

210
00:13:36,610 --> 00:13:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your eyes...</font>

211
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">look rosy in the right light, I suppose.</font>

212
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister, I'd like to have 
a chat with this girl.</font>

213
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said the lord's daughter was 
born sickly and won't live much longer.</font>

214
00:13:56,140 --> 00:14:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm going to play 
the part of Miss Cecilia.</font>

215
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why you?</font>

216
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said the lord had 
a secret child with a whore.</font>

217
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name happened to be Cecilia too,</font>

218
00:14:10,780 --> 00:14:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they put her in some orphanage 
right after she was born.</font>

219
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't he have the wrong girl?</font>

220
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, that description would fit—</font>

221
00:14:20,350 --> 00:14:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think he cares 
whether I'm the real one or not.</font>

222
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just happen to fit the bill.</font>

223
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that doesn't mean you have to...</font>

224
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says the lord will donate
 to the orphanage.</font>

225
00:14:35,180 --> 00:14:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you'll be just fine.</font>

226
00:14:55,110 --> 00:14:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother Natalie!</font>

227
00:14:56,830 --> 00:14:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lia! Pete! Everybody!</font>

228
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

229
00:15:03,590 --> 00:15:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cici...</font>

230
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cess?!</font>

231
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness! You're alive!</font>

232
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?!</font>

233
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault. I was such a fool.</font>

234
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?!</font>

235
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Luze was never going to let anyone 
who knew of his replacement daughter live.</font>

236
00:15:25,350 --> 00:15:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'd only realized sooner!</font>

237
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not your fault!</font>

238
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you walk? Where's everyone else?!</font>

239
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They killed them all. 
You're the only one I didn't see dead.</font>

240
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! We got a live one over here!</font>

241
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll flee out the back.</font>

242
00:15:52,470 --> 00:15:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are they?!</font>

243
00:15:53,430 --> 00:15:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going after them!</font>

244
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cess?!</font>

245
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on ahead! Call for help!</font>

246
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?!
 Come with me!</font>

247
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll never stop chasing you
 now that they've seen you!</font>

248
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be fine.</font>

249
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cess!</font>

250
00:16:23,420 --> 00:16:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go!</font>

251
00:16:38,180 --> 00:16:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All my hard work to find that pawn, 
only to have her broken so easily...</font>

252
00:16:44,370 --> 00:16:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was supposed to be at the mansion.</font>

253
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They never would've thought 
she'd be at the orphanage.</font>

254
00:16:50,610 --> 00:16:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all because Viscount Luze 
tried to take matters into his own hands.</font>

255
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobles of his ilk are all the same.</font>

256
00:16:58,450 --> 00:17:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this? A survivor?</font>

257
00:17:02,570 --> 00:17:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

258
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cici.</font>

259
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

260
00:17:08,690 --> 00:17:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A girl.</font>

261
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it,
 "Cici" was another nickname for Cecilia.</font>

262
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you have perfect rosy eyes.</font>

263
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mark of the Luze family.</font>

264
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I missed it because I took you for a boy.</font>

265
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got the sense that girl 
was hiding something.</font>

266
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I see it was you.</font>

267
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cess went with that lord to protect me!</i></font>

268
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you hate Viscount Luze?</font>

269
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case,</font>

270
00:17:44,770 --> 00:17:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what do you say I help you take revenge?</font>

271
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Revenge...?</font>

272
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you do as we say,</font>

273
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll let you make that lowlife 
suffer like you wouldn't believe.</font>

274
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just do what your heart tells you.</font>

275
00:18:03,220 --> 00:18:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you hate him?
 Don't you want to make him pay?</font>

276
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So just tear him down.</font>

277
00:18:10,080 --> 00:18:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this country with him.</font>

278
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You did it! That's my Cici!</i></font>

279
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Hey, quit it!</i></font>

280
00:18:19,670 --> 00:18:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's my fault. I was such a fool.</i></font>

281
00:18:21,930 --> 00:18:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's not your fault!</i></font>

282
00:18:27,910 --> 00:18:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to play 
the part of Miss Cecilia.</i></font>

283
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't...</i></font>

284
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>want to hear anyone's voice anymore.</i></font>

285
00:18:43,710 --> 00:18:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me. I've decided.</font>

286
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Decided what?</font>

287
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:55,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you. When to kill the O'Brian girl.</font>

288
00:18:56,050 --> 00:19:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought we might as well make it 
the day of Constance Grail's execution.</font>

289
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The day after tomorrow.</font>

290
00:19:03,930 --> 00:19:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

291
00:19:07,210 --> 00:19:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you find out anything about Rufus?</font>

292
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears the real Rufus May 
passed away ten years ago.</font>

293
00:19:16,250 --> 00:19:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was the youngest child 
of less-than-wealthy nobles.</font>

294
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He came to the capital when his bad 
conduct effectively got him disowned.</font>

295
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten years ago...</font>

296
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So they replaced him back then.</font>

297
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rest a little. I know you 
haven't been sleeping.</font>

298
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

299
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops. Am I interrupting something?</font>

300
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's all right.</font>

301
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I told you, Princess Alexandra
 of Faris opposes war.</font>

302
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't you like to see her 
accede to the throne?</font>

303
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your third princess has no lineage 
or support worth mentioning.</font>

304
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, isn't she a prisoner 
in Faris right now?</font>

305
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see what chance 
she has of winning out.</font>

306
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if she got herself 
a major backer?</font>

307
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if King Ernst only <i>said</i> he was 
going to talk trade with Melvina,</font>

308
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while really he went to Faris?</font>

309
00:20:24,650 --> 00:20:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

310
00:20:26,010 --> 00:20:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the king has no reason to go there.</font>

311
00:20:28,410 --> 00:20:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He could always say he's paying 
the king of Faris a get-well visit.</font>

312
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only the fact that the captive 
third princess invited him would matter.</font>

313
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Word would spread on its own.</font>

314
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Word that Adelbide is allied 
with the third princess.</font>

315
00:20:47,060 --> 00:20:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly. And just like that,
 she'd have support.</font>

316
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But isn't the third princess locked up?</font>

317
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is she going to invite the king?</font>

318
00:20:57,890 --> 00:21:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless... the princess 
in the tower is a double?</font>

319
00:21:03,190 --> 00:21:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on! You mean you're swaying 
the whole nation with a bluff?!</font>

320
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just goes to show how much 
Faris fears your country.</font>

321
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why didn't Crown Princess Cecilia 
give me any answer at all?</i></font>

322
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:21,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a visitor.</font>

323
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that you, Brenda?</font>

324
00:21:31,350 --> 00:21:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, um... What brings you here?</font>

325
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

326
00:21:37,130 --> 00:21:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kate and Mylene are 
protesting my execution?!</font>

327
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-They aren't alone.</font>

328
00:21:43,370 --> 00:21:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your father, your ex-fiancé Neil Bronson,
and Viscount Hamsworth are all helping.</font>

329
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the Earl of Ulster, of course.</font>

330
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Lordship!</i></font>

331
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, Brenda, when am I to be executed?</font>

332
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tomorrow, they say.</font>

333
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

334
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, I'm... thinking 
of accusing Pamela.</font>

335
00:22:13,050 --> 00:22:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll testify to everything
 she's ever done!</font>

336
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too little, too late, I know.</font>

337
00:22:19,860 --> 00:22:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've... I've been wanting 
to tell you something all this time.</font>

338
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for saving me back then.</font>

339
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't me, Brenda. It was—</font>

340
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it was you.</font>

341
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sincerity saved me.</font>

342
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not alone.</i></font>

343
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone is fighting for me.</i></font>

344
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll never give up.</i></font>

345
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After all...</i></font>

346
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure that's what Scarlett would say.</i></font>

347
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Arial"><font color="#511f35">Translation:
<font size="12">William Varteresian</font></font></font></font></font>

348
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:20,940
